                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18360404-1044-offence-1 t18360404-cd-154"></join>9th of April</rs>, 1 box, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., 3 lbs. of copper tubing, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18360404-name-1045" type="victimName">
